# Testing

- Put unit tests in `test/unit/`.
- Put widget tests in `test/widget/`.
- Put integration tests in `test/integration/`.
- Keep reusable fixtures in `test/helpers/` and fakes in `test/mocks/`.
- Add tests for critical domain logic and user-facing flows.
